
We are going to work on building data foundation for an on-demand Fitness app called DashFit. In this application, we have the following components:
Users sign up with the app to access video of the workout content.
There are multiple workout categories offered in the app e.g. Yoga, HIIT, Stretch.
Each category can have multiple classes offered under them. Each class will have 1 primary category but can belong to more than one category (e.g. Yoga & stretch).
There are trainers who record these classes, and one trainer can offer several different classes (yoga & HIIT from the same trainer).

Now, you are responsible for modeling the data foundation to track the success of this product.


